Hotel Sofitel Winter Palace, oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan 'Old Winter Palace Hotel', ayaa ah hudheel taariikhda gaaban oo 5-sano jir ah oo ku yaala magaalada Nile ee ku taal Luxor, Masar, koonfurta tuulada Luxor, oo leh 86 qol iyo 6 suuli.

